title: Aaron Bonner-Jackson
description: Pete's oldest friend Aaron Bonner-Jackson sit down with Sweet Lady Val and discuss junior high, high school and play never before heard tracks from their high school punk band "Nude" as well as one other special surprise. It's real, it's wonderful and very, very weird. Get into it!!
